  "detailed_description": "Each human is made up of several limbs and organs. Bacteria and other forms of microscopic life inhabit it. Your role as a disease will be to fight for survival! fight the cells on your way, evolve thanks to your ability to mutate and when you are ready, attack the organs to finish off your victim!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409700/extras/36387932e02bd6e34d19edb45b9deeff.poster.avif?t=1656520188\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409700/extras/36387932e02bd6e34d19edb45b9deeff.webm?t=1656520188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409700/extras/36387932e02bd6e34d19edb45b9deeff.mp4?t=1656520188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > contents </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A randomly generated body filled with rooms ready to be explored.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409700/extras/a5eb1382482815d11bf380341e0f67c4.poster.avif?t=1656520188\" width=504 height=826 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409700/extras/a5eb1382482815d11bf380341e0f67c4.webm?t=1656520188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409700/extras/a5eb1382482815d11bf380341e0f67c4.mp4?t=1656520188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> 5+ different diseases to unlock, each granting different objectives<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409700/extras/064dc4208422a3b5862056a5853fb844.poster.avif?t=1656520188\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409700/extras/064dc4208422a3b5862056a5853fb844.webm?t=1656520188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409700/extras/064dc4208422a3b5862056a5853fb844.mp4?t=1656520188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> 5+ unleashed bosses who will give everything not to be infected and to protect the body<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409700/extras/30865430617f9fe275600947d3699eb9.poster.avif?t=1656520188\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409700/extras/30865430617f9fe275600947d3699eb9.webm?t=1656520188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409700/extras/30865430617f9fe275600947d3699eb9.mp4?t=1656520188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> 50+ unique items making each game unique.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409700/extras/aae0da9de2a9a56457b18a74d2716986.poster.avif?t=1656520188\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409700/extras/aae0da9de2a9a56457b18a74d2716986.webm?t=1656520188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409700/extras/aae0da9de2a9a56457b18a74d2716986.mp4?t=1656520188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> An immune system taking the form of enemy and event! attack the body without paying attention and it will respond by reinforcing your opponents or pu